gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Cavaliers 121, Nuggets 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Cavaliers defeated the Mavericks, 121-109. Darius Garland recorded 26 points, six assists, and three rebounds for the Cavaliers, while Craig Porter added a career-high 21 points, and four assists in the victory. Michael Porter Jr. tallied 21 points and six rebounds for the Nuggets in the losing effort. The Cavaliers improve to 7-5 in the regular season, while the Nuggets fall to 9-4.
